Listing 4-36 Using latest method

latest_book = Book.objects.latest("published_date")
print(latest_book.title, latest_book.published_date)

Equivalent SQL

SELECT book.id, book.title, book.author_id, book.price,
book.number_of_pages, book.published_date,
book.created_at
FROM book
ORDER BY book.published_date DESC
LIMIT 1;